snippet.title: 11eyes ~ Tsumi to Batsu to Aganai no Shoujo CrossOver PSP Version PV HD
snippet.description:
11eyes CrossOver The opening theme to the PSP port 11eyes by Lass.

5pb is porting the Xbox 360 adventure game to PSP out in January 2010.

Artist: Ayane
Song: Shinjitsu e no Chinkonka
